<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF107-935-762  </DOCNO><DOCID>07 935 762.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>PC Week  Dec 4 1989 v6 n48 p29(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Ziff-Davis Publishing Co. 1989.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Dariana upgrades System Sleuth. (Dariana Technology Group Inc.)andO;</TITLE><AUTHOR>Sullivan, Kristina B.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Dariana Technology Group Inc. (product enhancement).andO;Product:   System Sleuth 2.0 (Performance analysis software) (productintroduction).andO;Topic:     EnhancementsUpgradingSoftware packagesDiagnostics.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>Dariana Upgrades System SleuthandM;Dariana Technology Group Inc. (DTG) last week began shipping an updatedversion of its System Sleuth diagnostic software, amid praise from earlyusers who said the software's new memory and hardware-interrupt functionsmake it a more thorough program.andM;System Sleuth version 2.0's new System Resources feature allows users to viewthe status of expanded memory, extended memory and hardware interrupt, saidofficials for the Buena Park, Calif., company.andM;Details on the status of extended and expanded memory help users to determinea system's configuration and to trouble-shoot potential conflicts, officialssaid.andP;  The ability to view the status of as many as 16 hardware-interruptlines enables users to target potential interrupt conflicts and to determinewhether installed devices are recognized by the system.andM;System Sleuth &quot;takes a good snapshot of what is in the machine,&quot; said GeorgeRoukas, advanced-systems manager for a Fortune 50 financial-services companyin New York.andP;  &quot;Information is in there about what vectors are in use and whatvectors are hooked by TSR [terminate-and-stay-resident] applications.&quot;andM;Roukas added that the software is a welcome relief from the &quot;old method ofpulling out the boards and looking for overlaps.&quot;andM;The upgraded program allows users to consolidate hardware and softwarediagnostics tools under the System Sleuth interface.andP;  Users can now access asmany as six third-party software utilities from within the System Sleuthmenu, officials said.andM;DTG can be reached at (714) 994-7400.andO;</TEXT></DOC>